      "level": 1,
      "content": "3.1 AI Tools Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "There are many AI tools available today, each with a different focus. Below is a breakdown by category:"
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontal-rule"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "🧑‍💻 Coding Related"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "listType": "unordered",
      "items": [
        "**ChatGPT**: General-purpose AI, supports code generation, explanation, and debugging, highly flexible.",
        "**Cursor**: An AI IDE built on VS Code, specialized for long code development and debugging.",
        "**Claude Code**: Handles very long context, suitable for large project code analysis.",
        "**GitHub Copilot**: Deeply integrated with GitHub/IDE, excels at code auto-completion.",
        "**Lovable**: AI-assisted site builder that can generate prototype websites in minutes."
      ]
    },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://chat.openai.com", "content": "ChatGPT Official Site" },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://cursor.sh", "content": "Cursor Official Site" },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://claude.ai", "content": "Claude Code Official Site" },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://github.com/features/copilot", "content": "GitHub Copilot Official Site" },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://lovable.dev", "content": "Lovable Official Site" },
    {
      "type": "horizontal-rule"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "🔍 Search / Research"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "listType": "unordered",
      "items": [
        "**Perplexity**: Real-time AI search engine with citations, suitable for academic research.",
        "**Grok (xAI)**: Integrates Twitter/X data, excels at real-time info and social media-related queries.",
        "**Google Gemini**: Google’s flagship AI, supports multimodal inputs (text, image, video)."
      ]
    },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://www.perplexity.ai", "content": "Perplexity Official Site" },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://x.ai", "content": "Grok Official Site" },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://gemini.google.com", "content": "Google Gemini Official Site" },
    {
      "type": "horizontal-rule"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "🎨 Design & Multimedia"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "listType": "unordered",
      "items": [
        "**Canva**: AI for graphic design, supports posters, presentations, and social media assets.",
        "**Kuse**: AI video generation tool, great for content creators."
      ]
    },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://www.canva.com", "content": "Canva Official Site" },
    { "type": "link", "title": "External Documentation", "href": "https://kuse.ai", "content": "Kuse Official Site" },
    {
      "type": "horizontal-rule"
    },
